JetSet.AI — UI/UX Design Document

Version: 1.0
Theme: Liquid Glass + Glassmorphism (Dark Immersive UI)
Tech Stack: React + TypeScript + Vite

1. Design Philosophy

JetSet AI uses a Liquid Glass design system that combines glassmorphism, depth, and motion to create a futuristic travel planning interface.

The design focuses on:

Liquid Glass UI

All UI elements behave like frosted translucent glass with layered blur and glow effects.

Properties:

translucency

blur

soft borders

glowing highlights

Deep Space Visual Style

The interface uses dark navy backgrounds with glowing accents to represent global travel at night.

Visual inspiration:

satellite imagery

city lights

aurora colors

Progressive Information Reveal

Travel information appears progressively as the AI generates the trip.

Examples:

staggered itinerary cards

streaming AI responses

skeleton loading states

